                    <p>• <strong>Stock Market:</strong> Moderate correlation (R = 0.67) with real estate investment</p>
                    <p>• <strong>Cost of Living:</strong> Direct impact on housing demand and purchasing power</p>
                </div>

                <div class="methodology">
                    <h3>Regression Model Performance</h3>
                    <p><strong>Multiple R:</strong> 0.995 | <strong>R²:</strong> 0.990 | <strong>Adjusted R²:</strong> 0.988</p>
                    <p><strong>F-statistic:</strong> 255.33 | <strong>p-value:</strong> < 0.001</p>
                    <p>The model explains 99% of the variance in residential property costs, indicating exceptional predictive power and statistical significance.</p>
